{"tid":1556093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葉德嫻心痛年輕人被打","createTime":"2019-09-09T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T15:01:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ada6362d46fadafed69a1541480127ea05425066","tid":1556093,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190909/20764703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190909%2F20764703&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=4ccbfb61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190909%2F20764703&h=a88cb69f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190909/20764703</a><br />\n<br />\n葉德嫻心痛年輕人被打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190909/large/1567953209_57f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190909%2Flarge%2F1567953209_57f6.jpg&h=e383638a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉德嫻昨日再次上街。<br />\n<br />\n逆權運動持續，葉德嫻、RubberBand成員泥鯭、阮民安和王宗堯昨日下午都參加了遮打花園的集會，隨人群步行到美國領事館。葉德嫻被問到有年輕人被警察打到重傷，可有心痛？她說：「你話呢？」不願停下來受訪的她，又不失幽默地問：「你可唔可以寫我疑似係你外婆嘅人？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190909/large/1567953207_2700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190909%2Flarge%2F1567953207_2700.jpg&h=f7794bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泥鯭跟隨大隊步行到美國領事館。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190909/large/1567953208_71ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190909%2Flarge%2F1567953208_71ec.jpg&h=4f2cb2ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王宗堯希望林鄭不要再扮有讓步空間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190909/large/1567953208_8ce5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190909%2Flarge%2F1567953208_8ce5.jpg&h=f27cea1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阮民安質疑陳百祥盲撐警。<br />\n<br />\n阮民安對於有示威年輕人被打感心痛，他說：「十個人打一個，頭都穿，但個小朋友眼神仲係堅定唔驚。」對於陳百祥撐警和解放軍，指「部隊及警察給我們安全」，他說：「我想佢睇吓近日啲片，冇特別裝備嘅年輕人都打到咁，你係咪盲X咗？」王宗堯對於黃之鋒昨日離港時在機場被捕，就懷疑他的法定出境日期被調轉，所以不能出境，他說：「我覺得呢啲都係林鄭嘅手法，表面好似釋出善意，但私下又用陰招。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190909/large/1567953209_ac2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190909%2Flarge%2F1567953209_ac2a.jpg&h=eb4601bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭富城昨晚駕車到銅鑼灣幫囡囡買尿片。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n此外，郭富城昨晚近7時駕車到銅鑼灣，他面露尷尬向記者表示：「我去買尿片畀個女呀！」當被追問對遊行的看法時，他未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：王連連<br />\n攝影：仇志德 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n祖昆《JOKER小丑》熱捧金獅<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n小環食店抹走紅油再開舖"}]}